==評價及獎項==
此劇集在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]網站上獲得普遍的好評，得分為65分（總分100）<ref>{{cite web|title=''Goliath'' - Season 1 Reviews|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/goliath|work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|accessdate=2017-01-09|archive-date=2022-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220222230905/https://www.metacritic.com/tv/goliath|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]網站上35位觀眾中有77%願意推薦，獲得了「Certified Fresh」的評價<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/goliath/s01/|title=''Goliath'': Season 1|work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=[[Fandango_(company)|Fandango]]|accessdate=2017-01-09|archive-date=2021-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211130032753/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/goliath/s01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

